<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= @event.eventtype.name %> Cancelled</h1>
    <p>
    Hi <%= @player.first_name %>, <br />
    This is to inform you that the <%= @event.eventtype.name %> scheduled for
    <%= @event.the_date %> at <%= @event.the_time.strftime('%H:%M:%S %P')%> <b> has been cancelled.</b><br />
    More information can be found be checking the schedule <%=link_to "here", @player.team %>
    </p>
    <p>
      This is an automated email. Please do not reply
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>